title: Agriculture Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Land Use' and process_sector1 == 'Agriculture' and commodity_type == 'Fuel'

title: Building Production by Sector
filter: varbl == 'production' and process_sector0 == 'Buildings' and commodity_real == 'Building' and scen == @df_lower.scen[0]

title: Commercial Buildings Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Buildings' and process_sector1 == 'Commercial' and commodity_type == 'Fuel'

title: Residential Buildings Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Buildings' and process_sector1 == 'Residential'

title: Industry Captured Emissions by Sector
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions' and process_sector0 == 'Industry'

title: Manufacturing Captured Emissions by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions' and process_sector1 == 'Manufacturing'

title: Power Generation Captured Emissions by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions' and process_sector0 == 'Power Generation'

title: Electricity Generation Capacity by Tech and Fuel
filter: varbl == 'capacity' and process_sector0 == 'Power Generation' and process_technology0 == 'Generation'

title: Electricity Generation Energy
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_real == 'Electricity' and process_sector0 == 'Power Generation' and not process_technology0 in ['Storage', 'Hydrogen Storage']

title: Electricity consumption by sector
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and commodity_real == 'Electricity' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic' and not process_sector0 == 'Power Generation'

title: Generation Emissions Intensity by Tech
filter: varbl == 'production' and process_sector0 == 'Power Generation' and ((commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') or (process_sector0 == 'Power Generation' and unit in ['TWh','PJ'] and not process_technology0 in ['Storage', 'Hydrogen Storage']))

title: Renewable Energy Fraction
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_real == 'Electricity' and process_sector0 == 'Power Generation' and not process_technology0 in ['Storage', 'Hydrogen Storage']

title: Storage Annual Discharge by Technology
filter: varbl == 'production' and process_sector0 == 'Power Generation' and process_technology0 in ['Storage', 'Hydrogen Storage'] and not process.str.contains('_charging', case=False)

title: Storage Capacity by Technology
filter: varbl == 'capacity' and process_technology0 in ['Storage', 'Hydrogen Storage'] and not process.str.contains('_discharging', case=False)

title: Agriculture Abatement By Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions' and process_sector1 == 'Agriculture'

title: Agriculture and Land Use Emissions
filter: varbl == 'production' and (commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') and process_sector0 == 'Land Use'

title: Aluminium Emissions by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and (commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') and process_sector2 == 'Aluminium'

title: Built Environment Emissions
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] and process_sector0 == 'Buildings'

title: Domestic Transport Emissions by Subsector
filter: varbl == 'production' and (commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: Emissions Reduction by Sector
filter: varbl == 'production' and (commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: Emissions from Electricity Generation
filter: varbl == 'production' and process_sector0 == 'Power Generation' and commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions']

title: Industry Captured Emissions
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions' and process_sector0 == 'Industry'

title: Iron and Steel Emissions
filter: varbl == 'production' and (commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') and process_sector2 == 'Iron & Steel'

title: Manufacturing Emissions by Sector
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_real == 'CO2' and process_sector1 == 'Manufacturing'

title: Resource Extraction Emissions by Sector
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] and process_sector1 == 'Mining'

title: Biomethane Production by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_real == 'Biomethane' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: commodity_fuel hierarchy
filter: ['commodity_fuel0', 'commodity_fuel1', commodity, commodity]

title: commodity_sector hierarchy
filter: ['commodity_sector0', 'commodity_sector1', 'commodity_sector2', commodity, commodity]

title: process_sector hierarchy
filter: ['process_sector0', 'process_sector1', 'process_sector2', process, process]

title: process_technology hierarchy
filter: ['process_technology0', 'process_technology1', process, process]

title: region hierarchy
filter: ['region_state0', 'region_state1', region, region]

title: Hydrogen Consumption by Sector
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and commodity_real == 'Hydrogen' and not process_technology0 in ['Storage', 'Hydrogen Storage']

title: Hydrogen Production by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_real == 'Hydrogen' and not process_technology0 in ['Storage', 'Hydrogen Storage']

title: Aluminium Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector2 == 'Aluminium' and commodity_type == 'Fuel'

title: Aluminium Production by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_real == 'Aluminium'

title: Industry Emissions and Captured Emissions
filter: varbl == 'production' and (commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') and process_sector0 == 'Industry'

title: Industry Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Industry' and commodity_type == 'Fuel'

title: Iron and Steel Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector2 == 'Iron & Steel' and commodity_type == 'Fuel'

title: Iron and Steel Production by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and process_sector2 == 'Iron & Steel' and commodity_type == 'Feedstock' and (commodity_real == 'Steel Slabs' | commodity_real == 'Sponge Iron' | commodity_real == 'Iron Ore Pig')

title: Agriculture and Land Use Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Land Use' and commodity_type == 'Fuel'

title: Chemical Captured Emissions by Process
filter: varbl == 'production' and commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions' and process_sector1 == 'Chemicals'

title: Net Emissions by Sector
filter: varbl == 'production' and (commodity_type in ['Combustion Emissions', 'Process Emissions'] or commodity_type == 'Captured Emissions') and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: Resource extraction sector energy use
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector1 == 'Mining' and commodity_type == 'Fuel'

title: Domestic Aviation Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector2 == 'Aviation' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: Domestic Shipping Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector2 == 'Shipping' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: Domestic Transport Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: International Aviation Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector2 == 'Aviation' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and jurisdiction == 'International'

title: International Shipping Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector2 == 'Shipping' and jurisdiction == 'International'

title: New Vehicle Sales by Drivetrain
filter: process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector1 == 'Road' and varbl == 'new_capacity'

title: New Vehicle Sales by Type
filter: varbl == 'new_capacity' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector1 == 'Road'

title: Rail Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector2 == 'Rail' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: Road Transport Energy Use by Fuel
filter: varbl == 'consumption' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector1 == 'Road' and jurisdiction == 'Domestic'

title: Road Vehicle Distance Travelled by Drivetrain
filter: varbl == 'production' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector1 == 'Road' and commodity_real == 'Passenger Transport km'

title: Road Vehicle Stock by drivetrain
filter: (varbl == 'capacity' or varbl == 'new_capacity') and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector1 == 'Road'

title: Vehicle Distance Travelled by Type
filter: varbl == 'production' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector1 == 'Road' and commodity_real == 'Passenger Transport km'

title: Vehicle Stock by Type
filter: varbl == 'capacity' and process_sector0 == 'Transport' and process_sector1 == 'Road'
